OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FM&S scraps 'best before'   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdates on fruit and veg to  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcut food waste             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Marks & Spencer is taking "best before"
OL,6, dates off more than 300 fruit and      
OL,7, vegetable items to tackle food waste.  
OL,9,FThey will be replaced by a code that   
OL,10,FM&S staff can use to check freshness   
OL,11,Fand quality.                           
OL,13,FTesco, Morrisons and Co-op are among   
OL,14,Fsupermarkets that have scrapped "use   
OL,15,Fby" dates on some of their products.   
OL,17,FWaste & Resources Action Programme     
OL,18,F(Wrap) said 70% of the UK's food waste 
OL,19,Fis binned in homes, mounting up to 4.5 
OL,20,Fmillion tonnes of edible food a year.  
